          <div>
            <p class="font-display font-bold text-stone-900 text-base">罗伯特·鲁宾</p>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-stone-400 mt-0.5">Robert Rubin · 1938–</p>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] bg-blue-50 text-blue-700 border border-blue-200 font-semibold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">政商旋转门</span>
